An. minimus
is the predominant species of the Minimus Complex in the Oriental Region. It is recorded from northeastern India to eastern China ( Taiwan ) and southward from Sichuan Province of China through Laos , Thailand , Vietnam and Cambodia (
Subbarao, 1998
;
Van Bortel et al ., 1999
,
2000
;
