). In comparison, available records indicate that
An. harrisoni
has a smaller, patchy distribution in Southeast Asia. Populations have been documented in south-central China (Chen et al ., 2002 ), central Myanmar (
Singh et al ., 2006
), northern and central Vietnam (
Van Bortel et al ., 1999
,
2000
